title: Week 15 Recap: Jets Refuse to Lose, Chiefs Can't Lose, Patriots Keep Losing | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Kevin and Nora react to the New York Jets' first win of the season and how it affects their chances for Trevor Lawrence (1:00), name their winners and losers of Week 15 (17:45), go through the Hurry Up (1:06:10), answer listeners' questions (1:08:23), and pick their clickbait headlines of the week (1:14:22).

Hosts: Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti
